==Translingual==
===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[papilio]], butterfly

===Proper noun===
'''''Papilionaceae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] of a [[family]], with as the allowed alternate ''[[Fabaceae]]''. [[Circumscription]] of this group may vary with [[taxonomic]] viewpoint. This same group may be treated in the rank of subfamily: the ''[[Papilionoideae]]'' of family ''[[Leguminosae]]''. 

